## Installation

You can install _{{friendly_name}}_ via [pip] from [PyPI]. The package is distributed as a pure Python package, but also with pre-compiled wheels for major platforms, which include performance optimizations.

```console
$ pip install {{project_name}}
```

The pre-compiled wheels are built using `mypyc` and will be used automatically if your platform is supported. You can check the files on PyPI to see the list of available wheels.

